<div data-controller="appear">
  <h1 class="type-display-punjabi text-center animate-fade-in-up" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Travel</h1>
  <p class="text-center animate-fade-in-up delay-1" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">Getting to Orange County, California</p>

  <div class="space-y-8">
    <div class="appear" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
        All weekend events are in Orange County, Southern California. The JW Marriott Anaheim Resort is the home base — located steps from Disneyland and about 20 minutes from the Gurudwara in Buena Park.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="card appear" style="overflow: hidden; padding: 0; border-radius: var(--radius-md);">
      <iframe
        src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=JW+Marriott+Anaheim+Resort+1775+S+Disneyland+Dr+Anaheim+CA+92802&output=embed"
        width="100%"
        height="400"
        style="border:0;"
        allowfullscreen=""
        loading="lazy"
        referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
      </iframe>
    </section>

    <!-- Airports -->
    <section class="card appear">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">Airports</h2>

        <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">
          <h3 style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: var(--space-1);">John Wayne Airport (SNA) — Recommended</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: var(--space-1);">~15 minutes from JW Marriott</p>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Orange County's closest airport. Flights from major US hubs including SFO, SEA, DFW, ORD, and more. Easiest in and out — no LA traffic.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">
          <h3 style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: var(--space-1);">Los Angeles International (LAX)</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: var(--space-1);">~45 minutes from JW Marriott (traffic-dependent)</p>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Best for international arrivals and the widest selection of routes and airlines. Budget extra time for LA traffic.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">
          <h3 style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: var(--space-1);">Long Beach Airport (LGB)</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: var(--space-1);">~30 minutes from JW Marriott</p>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Smaller and stress-free. JetBlue and Southwest service. A great option if fares are competitive.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: var(--space-1);">Hollywood Burbank Airport (BUR)</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: var(--space-1);">~50 minutes from JW Marriott</p>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Good option if flying from Northern California or on Southwest. Smaller and easier than LAX.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Ceremony Day Shuttle -->
    <section class="card appear" style="border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Ceremony Day Shuttle</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">
          On Friday, November 27, a shuttle will run from the JW Marriott to Singh Sabha Gurudwara in Buena Park for the Anand Karaj ceremony. Departure is at <strong>8:00 AM</strong> from the hotel entrance.
        </p>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
          Return shuttles will be provided after Langar (approximately 2:00 PM). If you plan to drive yourself, parking is available at the Gurudwara.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Getting Around -->
    <section class="card appear">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Getting Around</h2>

        <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">
          <h3 style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: var(--space-1);">Rideshare</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Uber and Lyft are widely available throughout Orange County. This is the easiest option for getting between the hotel, Gurudwara, and local spots.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">
          <h3 style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: var(--space-1);">Rental Car</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Recommended if you plan to explore the coast, head into LA, or venture to Artesia (Little India). All major rental agencies are available at SNA and LAX.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: var(--space-1);">Walking</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">The JW Marriott is walkable to Disneyland, Downtown Disney, and nearby restaurants and shops. You may not need a car at all if you're staying at the hotel.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Travel Notes -->
    <section class="card appear">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Travel Notes</h2>
        <ul style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); list-style: disc; padding-left: var(--space-6);">
          <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">November weather in Orange County is mild and sunny — expect 65–75°F during the day and cooler evenings. A light jacket is all you'll need.</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Thanksgiving is November 26 — one of the busiest travel weeks of the year. Book flights early and budget extra time at the airport.</li>
          <li>Hotel parking is available at the JW Marriott (valet and self-parking). If driving to the Gurudwara, free parking is available on site.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>
